maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday afternoon’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Pick 4 Day” game were:
2-0-2-4, Wild: 7
(two, zero, two, four; Wild: seven)
